Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得紧张吗？殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(550,550)}亚特罗帕提尼平原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,100)}帕尔斯国 万骑长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}卡兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪 毕竟对殿下来说是初次上阵  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次战斗由安德拉寇拉斯陛下亲自出阵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将军巴夫利斯大人也坐镇于旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且除了我之外
